Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,do the worst case scenario scenario.\N{\rChinese}做最坏的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.36,English,,0,0,0,,We can't beat him up. What we'll do is just run away\N{\rChinese}我们没法打败他。我们要做的就是跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.24,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? So\N{\rChinese}好的，这样说通吗？于是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.10,English,,0,0,0,,we don't think portion is an explanation\N{\rChinese}我们认为部分也不是解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,Because there's so many ways for us to fight back\N{\rChinese}因为有很多方法可以反击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.20,English,,0,0,0,,and to rebel against\N{\rChinese}并且可以反叛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.36,English,,0,0,0,,bigger people, okay so\N{\rChinese}更大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.40,English,,0,0,0,,Quarantine doesn't really work war\N{\rChinese}隔离并不真正起作用于战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so\N{\rChinese}好了，接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,We don't think war is a good explanation either\N{\rChinese}我们也认为战争不是一个好的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:27.88,English,,0,0,0,,So it is true that chimpanzees are\N{\rChinese}于是，黑猿确实是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.48,English,,0,0,0,,Naturally violent. Okay, they're always being the crap out of each other\N{\rChinese}他们总是互相打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.54,English,,0,0,0,,But guess what? bonobos\N{\rChinese}但你猜怎么了？狒猴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:41.38,English,,0,0,0,,Who are actually closer to us genetically than chimpanzees?\N{\rChinese}谁在基因上比黑猿更接近我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.32,English,,0,0,0,,They're actually very peaceful.\N{\rChinese}它们实际上非常和平。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.40,English,,0,0,0,,They don't fight each other\N{\rChinese}它们互相不打架。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:50.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so there's no evidence that we human beings are\N{\rChinese}好的，已经没有证据表明我们人类本身是自然的暴力者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.40,English,,0,0,0,,naturally violent\N{\rChinese}也就是说如果是战争的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.72,English,,0,0,0,,Also if it is war\N{\rChinese}Also if it is war
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:03.08,English,,0,0,0,,then we should be able to find weapons\N{\rChinese}然后我们应该能找到武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.00,English,,0,0,0,,And we don't really find weapons,\N{\rChinese}而我们确实没找到武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:11.42,English,,0,0,0,,okay in archaeology We don't really find weapons of early human history\N{\rChinese}在考古学里我们确实没找到早期人类的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.92,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.88,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay okay okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:32.96,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的好的好的好的好的好的好的好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.28,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay okay okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.22,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.20,English,,0,0,0,,okay okay okay\N{\rChinese}好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.26,English,,0,0,0,,Now it's possible that in the future we'll find evidence,\N{\rChinese}现在有可能在未来我们会找到证据，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:48.40,English,,0,0,0,,but I'm just saying that right now, in archeology and anthropology,\N{\rChinese}但我现在只是说，在考古学和人类学里，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.88,English,,0,0,0,,we do not have any evidence, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们还没有任何证据，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:55.00,English,,0,0,0,,The last, then we look at respect for elders.\N{\rChinese}最后，我们再看对长辈的敬重。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.32,English,,0,0,0,,And even though this is a valid theory,\N{\rChinese}即便这是一种有效的理论，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.64,English,,0,0,0,,there's an argument that back\N{\rChinese}还有一种反驳说回……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.08,English,,0,0,0,,then they didn't really care about dying that much.\N{\rChinese}然后他们并不太在意死亡。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.74,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why is that\N{\rChinese}原因是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.40,English,,0,0,0,,for most of human history,\N{\rChinese}在大部分人类历史里，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:17.46,English,,0,0,0,,we human beings have seen life,\N{\rChinese}我们人类已经把生命看成一个圆环，没错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.82,English,,0,0,0,,history as a circle, right?\N{\rChinese}比如说，现在是夏天，……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:24.96,English,,0,0,0,,So for example, right now it's summer,\N{\rChinese}So for example, right now it's summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.00,English,,0,0,0,,it's gonna turn into fall, then winter, then spring,\N{\rChinese}它会变成秋天，然后是冬天，再是春天，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.10,English,,0,0,0,,then summer again, okay?\N{\rChinese}然后又是夏天，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.46,English,,0,0,0,,So the world, history,\N{\rChinese}于是世界，历史，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.14,English,,0,0,0,,moves in a cycle.\N{\rChinese}它在循环中移动。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.58,English,,0,0,0,,Well human life also moves in a cycle.\N{\rChinese}人类的生命也在循环中移动。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.66,English,,0,0,0,,You're born, you're born, you die,\N{\rChinese}你出生，你出生，你死亡。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.48,English,,0,0,0,,then you're reborn,\N{\rChinese}然后你重生，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.78,English,,0,0,0,,then you die again, then you're reborn again, okay?\N{\rChinese}然后你再次死亡，再次重生，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.76,English,,0,0,0,,So back then, they really didn't care if you died.\N{\rChinese}于是回到那时，他们真的不在乎你是否死亡。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.64,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, if you're an old person, you're probably like,\N{\rChinese}实际上，如果你是老人，可能会是这样，我更愿意死去，那么如果我死了，我就会重生或进入灵界，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,you know what, I'd rather be dead, and then,\N{\rChinese}实际上，如果你是老人，可能会是这样，我更愿意死去，那么如果我死了，我就会重生或进入灵界，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.30,English,,0,0,0,,so if I die, I'll either be reborn or go into the spirit world, okay?\N{\rChinese}实际上，如果你是老人，可能会是这样，我更愿意死去，那么如果我死了，我就会重生或进入灵界，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:04.70,English,,0,0,0,,So they didn't really fear death, or they really didn't see death like the way we saw death.\N{\rChinese}于是他们对死亡并不真正恐惧，也不把死亡看成我们所见的那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.22,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What is the evidence for death?\N{\rChinese}嗯？死亡的证据是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a great question, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的，这是个很好的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.74,English,,0,0,0,,So the evidence for this is what we understand about their religion,\N{\rChinese}因此，这一证据来自我们对他们宗教的理解，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.72,English,,0,0,0,,which we will discuss later on and in next class, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们稍后在下一节课里再讨论，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:22.00,English,,0,0,0,,All right, the last, so that leaves religion\N{\rChinese}好了，最后一个，剩下的是宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.56,English,,0,0,0,,as the most likely possibility.\N{\rChinese}作为最有可能的情况。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:31.68,English,,0,0,0,,And this, again, this is what most scholars believe happen.\N{\rChinese}再说一次，这就是大多数学者认为发生的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.42,English,,0,0,0,,And so we're gonna look at three different archeological sites.\N{\rChinese}于是我们将去看三个不同的考古遗址。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.34,English,,0,0,0,,The first is Copeca Tepe.\N{\rChinese}第一个是科佩卡塔佩。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:42.72,English,,0,0,0,,The second is Jericho. And the third is Catahoyac, okay?\N{\rChinese}第二个是耶利哥。第三个是卡塔霍亚克，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:47.84,English,,0,0,0,,All right, so I'm gonna draw up a,\N{\rChinese}好了，我要画一个……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.94,English,,0,0,0,,we'll first see a picture of Copeca Tepe.\N{\rChinese}我们先来看看科佩卡塔佩的照片。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.98,English,,0,0,0,,And guys, these places were only discovered\N{\rChinese}伙计们，这些地方是最近几十年才被发现的。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:06.76,English,,0,0,0,,in the past few decades,\N{\rChinese}in the past fewdecades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:11.14,English,,0,0,0,,okay? So these are new places. We're only starting to understand these places.\N{\rChinese}好的？这些是新发现的地方。我们才刚开始了解它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:15.62,English,,0,0,0,,And so this place is in Turkey, in central Turkey.\N{\rChinese}这个地方在土耳其中部。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.30,English,,0,0,0,,And this dates back to about 9500 BC.\N{\rChinese}它的年代约在公元前9500年。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.24,English,,0,0,0,,So this is about over 11,000 years old.\N{\rChinese}于是，这个地方已有11000多年的历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.38,English,,0,0,0,,And we don't even think this is the oldest place, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们甚至不认为它是最古老的地方，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.42,English,,0,0,0,,So if you did your research, you will know that\N{\rChinese}如果你做过研究，你就会知道。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:32.12,English,,0,0,0,,this is basically a place of religious worship.\N{\rChinese}这基本是一个宗教崇拜的场所。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:36.36,English,,0,0,0,,You can see that they constructed this place\N{\rChinese}你可以看到他们建造了这个场所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.34,English,,0,0,0,,so that there are these T -shaped holes.\N{\rChinese}于是出现了这些T形孔洞。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.64,English,,0,0,0,,These are the T -shaped pillars, okay? And these things are huge, right?\N{\rChinese}这些是T形柱子，行吗？这些东西很大，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:45.14,English,,0,0,0,,This is a human being and this is a T -shaped pillar, okay?\N{\rChinese}这是一个人，这是一根T形柱子，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:48.52,English,,0,0,0,,We think, again, this is all theory, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们认为，这又是理论，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.82,English,,0,0,0,,This is all what we know.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们所知的一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.46,English,,0,0,0,,We don't know that much because this is all recent, okay? But we think that\N{\rChinese}我们不太清楚，因为这只是最近的事，行吗？但我们认为……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:59.90,English,,0,0,0,,these T -shapes represent human beings,\N{\rChinese}这些T形结构代表人类。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.96,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And within these T -shapes are animals.\N{\rChinese}好的？在这些T形结构里还有动物。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.50,English,,0,0,0,,And you can see that they align,\N{\rChinese}你可以看到它们排列着，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,you know, they're not, you know, they're not exactly the same.\N{\rChinese}你知道，它们不是完全一样的。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.66,English,,0,0,0,,This is where we think that that makes sense.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们认为有意义的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:16.02,English,,0,0,0,,This is where we think that that makes sense. This is where we think that that makes sense.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们认为有意义的地方。这就是我们认为有意义的地方。
