Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.68,English,,0,0,0,,This is where we think that that makes sense.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们认为有意义的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.02,English,,0,0,0,,is a place of religious worship.\N{\rChinese}是一个宗教崇拜的场所。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,Now what's interesting about Gobeitepe is\N{\rChinese}现在，关于Gobeitepe有趣的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.24,English,,0,0,0,,that the religious site is the oldest,\N{\rChinese}那座宗教场所是最古老的，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:51.66,English,,0,0,0,,but we also find houses that are built later on.\N{\rChinese}但我们也发现后期建造的房屋。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:56.74,English,,0,0,0,,So what we think might have happened here is that\N{\rChinese}于是我们认为这里可能发生了……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:01.80,English,,0,0,0,,hunter -gatherers will come to a place now\N{\rChinese}猎人-采集者会来到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.12,English,,0,0,0,,and then to practice religion because\N{\rChinese}然后去实践宗教，因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.36,English,,0,0,0,,ultimately as human beings,\N{\rChinese}最终作为人类，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.58,English,,0,0,0,,and we discussed this last class,\N{\rChinese}我们在上节课讨论过这个问题，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:14.48,English,,0,0,0,,we have a yearning or we have a need to understand why.\N{\rChinese}我们有一种渴求或需要去理解它的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:17.28,English,,0,0,0,,And religion solves this problem for us.\N{\rChinese}宗教为我们解决了这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.48,English,,0,0,0,,Also, as hunter -gatherer,\N{\rChinese}另外，作为猎人-采集者，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:24.66,English,,0,0,0,,you need to associate with other hunter -gatherers in order to find mates,\N{\rChinese}你需要与其他猎人-采集者结伴，以便寻找配偶，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,to find husbands and wives to reproduce.\N{\rChinese}以便找到丈夫和妻子来繁衍。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.96,English,,0,0,0,,And so this sort of religious center, it's a great time to come\N{\rChinese}于是这类宗教中心，来此练习信仰正是好时机，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.76,English,,0,0,0,,and practice your religion, but\N{\rChinese}但也是聚餐的好时机。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.70,English,,0,0,0,,it's also a great time to feast and\N{\rChinese}it's also a great time to feast and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.58,English,,0,0,0,,to meet someone you can marry and have children with.\N{\rChinese}去遇见可以结婚并生孩子的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.34,English,,0,0,0,,So that\N{\rChinese}于是如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:46.86,English,,0,0,0,,was the original function of the temple.\N{\rChinese}这就是寺庙最初的功能。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:53.10,English,,0,0,0,,Now these places are often led by shamans.\N{\rChinese}现在这些地方往往由巫师领袖。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:58.08,English,,0,0,0,,And what makes them special is that they are charismatic leaders.\N{\rChinese}而使它们特别的，是它们是有魅力的领袖。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:01.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Charismatic leaders.\N{\rChinese}好？有魅力的领袖。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.48,English,,0,0,0,,Charismatic leaders are people like Mao Zedong,\N{\rChinese}具有魅力的领袖像毛泽东、巴拉克·奥巴马、比尔·克林顿，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.56,English,,0,0,0,,Barack Obama, Bill Clinton, okay?\N{\rChinese}他们是那种人，因各种原因，...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.98,English,,0,0,0,,They're people who for whatever reason,\N{\rChinese}They're people whofor whatever reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:14.86,English,,0,0,0,,people just love them and want to follow them.\N{\rChinese}人们只是喜欢他们，想跟随他们。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:19.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And so maybe what happened was\N{\rChinese}好？于是也许是这样发生的。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,that these charismatic leaders,\N{\rChinese}这些有魅力的领袖，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:25.72,English,,0,0,0,,they built this place and they became like celebrities.\N{\rChinese}他们建造了这个地方，随后便成了名人。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:29.68,English,,0,0,0,,And people came from all over to meet them,\N{\rChinese}人们从四面八方赶来与他们相会，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:31.30,English,,0,0,0,,to hear the religion,\N{\rChinese}去聆听那宗教的教义。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.32,English,,0,0,0,,and to meet other people.\N{\rChinese}并与其他人相会。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.10,English,,0,0,0,,And over time,\N{\rChinese}并且随着时间的推移，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.66,English,,0,0,0,,some people even chose to stay with them\N{\rChinese}有些人甚至选择与他们同住。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:42.94,English,,0,0,0,,and build houses to celebrate them.\N{\rChinese}建造房屋以庆祝他们。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And then when they died,\N{\rChinese}好了？随后他们去世后，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:50.80,English,,0,0,0,,what happened was they still worshiped them in their death.\N{\rChinese}所发生的事是他们仍在死后祭祀他们。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:54.50,English,,0,0,0,,And so this place became a temple.\N{\rChinese}于是这地方变成了寺庙。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? So\N{\rChinese}好？这有道理吗？于是……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.70,English,,0,0,0,,that's one theory about Kobayatepe.\N{\rChinese}这就是关于科巴亚特佩的一个理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:02.14,English,,0,0,0,,There are other theories. Okay?\N{\rChinese}还有其他理论。好？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:06.82,English,,0,0,0,,There are some people who will tell you that space aliens came down\N{\rChinese}有些人会告诉你，外星人降临并建造了这个地方，因为它很精巧。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:09.88,English,,0,0,0,,and built this place because it's so sophisticated.\N{\rChinese}and built this place because it's so sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But, so there are different theories.\N{\rChinese}好？但，确实有不同的理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:17.24,English,,0,0,0,,But the one that scholars most agree with today,\N{\rChinese}但目前学者最一致的说法是，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.60,English,,0,0,0,,okay, is that it was a religious center.\N{\rChinese}好，认为它是一个宗教中心。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:26.66,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions before I move on to, before I move on?\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？我继续讲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:32.74,English,,0,0,0,,So this means that religions were honored?\N{\rChinese}这意味着宗教被尊崇了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:34.46,English,,0,0,0,,Yes. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的，答案是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:35.86,English,,0,0,0,,So that's a great question.\N{\rChinese}那是个很好的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:38.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Where does religion come from?\N{\rChinese}好？宗教从哪里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.58,English,,0,0,0,,And this is something that we will look at very closely next class.\N{\rChinese}接下来一节课我们会仔细研究这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:43.56,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is this.\N{\rChinese}答案就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.42,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Even though\N{\rChinese}好的。虽然如此，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:49.44,English,,0,0,0,,we all have the need for religion,\N{\rChinese}我们都需要宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:53.46,English,,0,0,0,,we don't all have the ability to produce religion.\N{\rChinese}我们并非都具备创作宗教的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So who these charismatic leaders are,\N{\rChinese}好？那么这些有魅力的领袖是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:58.34,English,,0,0,0,,are people who\N{\rChinese}他们就是人们……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:24:02.38,English,,0,0,0,,have visions or dreams of God.\N{\rChinese}有关于上帝的异象或梦境。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:04.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Or the spirit world.\N{\rChinese}好？或者关于灵界的异象。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:08.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And then they present their visions to other people.\N{\rChinese}好？随后他们把自己的异象呈现给他人。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:11.28,English,,0,0,0,,And we have people like this throughout human history.\N{\rChinese}我们在整个人类历史中都有类似的人物。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So think of Jesus.\N{\rChinese}好？想想耶稣。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.54,0:24:14.78,English,,0,0,0,,Think of Mohammed.\N{\rChinese}想想穆罕默德。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,Think of Buddha. Think of Confucius.\N{\rChinese}想想佛陀。想想孔子。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.84,English,,0,0,0,,Right? These are people who\N{\rChinese}好？这些人是……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:28.34,English,,0,0,0,,have these visions of God or of spirituality\N{\rChinese}他们拥有关于上帝或灵性的异象。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:31.38,English,,0,0,0,,or of a new world and present to people.\N{\rChinese}或是新世界的愿景并呈现给人们。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:35.22,English,,0,0,0,,And because they're charismatic, they're able to attract followers and spread their religion.\N{\rChinese}而且因为他们有魅力，能吸引追随者并传播其宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:38.72,English,,0,0,0,,And that's what probably happened here as well.\N{\rChinese}这大概也是此处所发生的情形。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:41.08,English,,0,0,0,,Because as you can see from this picture,\N{\rChinese}因为从这张图可以看出，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.26,0:24:46.28,English,,0,0,0,,it was very hard work to build this temple.\N{\rChinese}建这座寺庙是一件非常艰苦的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:49.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is 11,000 years ago.\N{\rChinese}好了？这已经是11000年前的事了。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.02,0:24:51.78,English,,0,0,0,,They didn't have bulldozers.\N{\rChinese}他们没有推土机。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:53.34,English,,0,0,0,,They didn't have shovels.\N{\rChinese}他们没有铲子。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is all by hand.\N{\rChinese}好了？全靠手工。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.06,0:25:00.88,English,,0,0,0,,So for them to want to dedicate their lives to building this temple,\N{\rChinese}于是他们愿意把一生奉献给建这座寺庙，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.96,0:25:02.38,English,,0,0,0,,because it took a long time.\N{\rChinese}因为这需要很长时间。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.38,0:25:06.18,English,,0,0,0,,It took years and years and hundreds of people.\N{\rChinese}耗费了多年，数百人。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.52,0:25:09.74,English,,0,0,0,,Well, you needed something called religious devotion.\N{\rChinese}好吧，你们需要一种叫做宗教奉献的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.32,0:25:12.68,English,,0,0,0,,Faith. Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}信仰。这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.24,0:25:16.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And again, throughout human history, we've seen this.\N{\rChinese}好的？再说一次，纵观人类历史，我们都看到了这一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:18.56,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So think of Christians. Think of Buddhists.\N{\rChinese}对吧？想想基督徒。想想佛教徒。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:20.26,English,,0,0,0,,Think of Muslims.\N{\rChinese}想想穆斯林。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.66,0:25:23.54,English,,0,0,0,,Religious faith. So that's what built this.\N{\rChinese}宗教信仰。于是这才建成。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.18,0:25:26.20,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So does that answer your question?\N{\rChinese}好的？那就回答了你的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.42,0:25:29.28,English,,0,0,0,,Yes. Okay. Any more questions before I continue?\N{\rChinese}是。好的。继续之前还有别的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:34.58,English,,0,0,0,,Yes?.\N{\rChinese}是？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:44.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So that's a good question.\N{\rChinese}好的。那是个好问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.28,0:25:47.34,English,,0,0,0,,Why is a temple structured like this?\N{\rChinese}为什么寺庙会这样结构？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the answer is that\N{\rChinese}好的？答案是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.04,0:25:55.00,English,,0,0,0,,there's cosmological significance\N{\rChinese}有宇宙学意义
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.00,0:25:56.28,English,,0,0,0,,to the structure.\N{\rChinese}在结构中。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.60,0:25:59.98,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that on a certain time of the year,\N{\rChinese}意味着在一年中的某个时刻，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.98,0:26:02.68,English,,0,0,0,,what will happen is that\N{\rChinese}事情会是这样：太阳会以某种方式照射到这个地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.68,0:26:05.86,English,,0,0,0,,the sun will hit this place in a certain way.\N{\rChinese}于是它几乎像个钟表。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,So it's almost like a clock.\N{\rChinese}这就是它的作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.10,0:26:09.30,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense to you guys?\N{\rChinese}你们觉得这样有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:12.70,English,,0,0,0,,They designed this in a way so they can tell time.\N{\rChinese}他们把它设计成可以用来计时的样子。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:15.48,English,,0,0,0,,But their intention was not to tell time.\N{\rChinese}但他们的目的并不是用来计时。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.62,0:26:19.14,English,,0,0,0,,Their intention was to connect with the outer world.\N{\rChinese}他们的意图是与外部世界相连。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.90,0:26:21.52,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Does that make sense to you guys?\N{\rChinese}对吧？你们觉得这样有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.82,0:26:23.48,English,,0,0,0,,So they were extremely sophisticated.\N{\rChinese}于是他们非常精巧。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:26.64,English,,0,0,0,,They knew a lot about the way the stars worked.\N{\rChinese}他们对星星的运行方式了解很多。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.64,0:26:31.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So basically, for them, this is science.\N{\rChinese}好吧？基本上，对他们来说，这就是科学。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.64,0:26:34.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Today we say this is a religion.\N{\rChinese}好吧？今天我们说这是一种宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.70,0:26:38.20,English,,0,0,0,,But their science back then is no different from our science today.\N{\rChinese}但当时的科学和今天的科学没有区别。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:40.00,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that answer your question?\N{\rChinese}好吧？这回答了你的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.38,0:26:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. And you had a question? .\N{\rChinese}好的。你还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.36,0:26:54.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So if you talk to any religious people, they saw it.\N{\rChinese}好的。只要你跟任何宗教人士说话，他们就会看到它。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:56.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They were there.\N{\rChinese}好的？他们就在那儿。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.34,0:26:58.18,English,,0,0,0,,They talked to God. Right?\N{\rChinese}他们跟上帝说话。对吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.18,0:27:01.52,English,,0,0,0,,So we're like, well, you know, that doesn't make any sense.\N{\rChinese}于是我们说，嗯，你知道，这样说没啥意义。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:03.34,English,,0,0,0,,But they really believe it.\N{\rChinese}但他们真的相信。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:05.60,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why they're able to convince their followers.\N{\rChinese}这就是他们能说服众的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.50,0:27:09.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So in the future, we will look at someone like Muhammad\N{\rChinese}好的？那么在未来，我们会去看像穆罕默德这样的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:12.20,English,,0,0,0,,who had religious visions in a cave.\N{\rChinese}他在洞里有宗教异象。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.78,0:27:15.74,English,,0,0,0,,And you're like, did he really see an angel?\N{\rChinese}你会问，他真的看见天使了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.94,0:27:17.30,English,,0,0,0,,Well, he thought he really did.\N{\rChinese}好吧，他真的以为自己做到了。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:21.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And\N{\rChinese}好？而且
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.66,0:27:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,in fact, in our research,\N{\rChinese}事实上，在我们的研究中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.26,0:27:28.16,English,,0,0,0,,what we discovered is that people who use something called the\N{\rChinese}我们发现的是，使用一种叫做“迷幻剂”的人。好？你知道迷幻剂是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.68,0:27:30.98,English,,0,0,0,,psychedelics. Okay? Do you know what psychedelics are?\N{\rChinese}迷幻剂是药物。是什么药物？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.86,0:27:35.90,English,,0,0,0,,Psychedelics are drugs. What drugs, and\N{\rChinese}Psychedelics are drugs. What drugs, and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.90,0:27:41.80,English,,0,0,0,,what these drugs do is they shift your neural system\N{\rChinese}这些药物的作用是让你的神经系统发生变化，从而你以不同的方式感知世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.80,0:27:44.76,English,,0,0,0,,so that you see the world in a different way.\N{\rChinese}当你这样做时，你就能看到不同的景象。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.88,0:27:47.18,English,,0,0,0,,When you do that, you're able to have different visions.\N{\rChinese}When you do that, you're able to have different visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.28,0:27:49.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But we also know that\N{\rChinese}好的？但我们也知道，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.86,0:27:54.84,English,,0,0,0,,if you go hungry for a long time or you meditate for a long time,\N{\rChinese}如果你长时间饿着或者长时间冥想，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.88,0:27:56.32,English,,0,0,0,,you're able to see different things.\N{\rChinese}你就能看到不同的事物。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.32,0:27:59.24,English,,0,0,0,,So from their perspective, they actually saw this thing.\N{\rChinese}从他们的视角来看，他们确实看到了这件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.96,0:28:03.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Even though like we don't think it actually happened.\N{\rChinese}好？虽然我们觉得这件事并未真正发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.32,0:28:05.74,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? For them, it's true.\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？对他们来说，这是真的。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.96,0:28:07.56,English,,0,0,0,,But maybe for us, it's not so true.\N{\rChinese}但对我们来说，可能并非如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:12.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right. Any more questions before I go on?\N{\rChinese}好？好了。还有别的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.84,0:28:16.34,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So\N{\rChinese}好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.34,0:28:20.12,English,,0,0,0,,these are great questions.\N{\rChinese}这些是很好的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.32,0:28:22.40,English,,0,0,0,,And keep on asking them.\N{\rChinese}继续问下去。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.46,0:28:26.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And these are hard questions that we will go over the next few classes.\N{\rChinese}好的，这些是我们接下来几节课要讨论的难题。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.30,0:28:29.38,English,,0,0,0,,So let me show you another picture. Okay?\N{\rChinese}好了，我再给你展示一张图。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.22,0:28:36.46,English,,0,0,0,,This is what is in the pillars at Goblete Tepe.\N{\rChinese}这就是在戈布莱特佩柱子里的样子。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.88,0:28:39.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now,\N{\rChinese}好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.50,0:28:42.40,English,,0,0,0,,what's really interesting about these pictures,\N{\rChinese}这些图像真正有趣的地方是……
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.50,0:28:45.76,English,,0,0,0,,okay, is that these are animals\N{\rChinese}好了，关键是这些是动物……
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.46,0:28:49.20,English,,0,0,0,,in the motion of hunting.\N{\rChinese}它们正处于狩猎动作中。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:51.14,English,,0,0,0,,So the fox, right?\N{\rChinese}所以狐狸，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.38,0:28:55.44,English,,0,0,0,,The way the fox hunts is the fox jumps up in the air\N{\rChinese}狐狸的捕猎方式是先跳到空中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,and then goes down. And attacks the prey.\N{\rChinese}然后落下，攻击猎物。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.08,0:29:01.94,English,,0,0,0,,So this is in the motion of attack.\N{\rChinese}于是它们正处于攻击动作中。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.50,0:29:03.56,English,,0,0,0,,Why would they do that?\N{\rChinese}他们为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.46,0:29:09.74,English,,0,0,0,,What's the point of having animals on these pillars?\N{\rChinese}把动物放在这些柱子上有什么意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.30,0:29:11.34,English,,0,0,0,,Why would they do that?\N{\rChinese}他们为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.86,0:29:19.24,English,,0,0,0,,Good. Okay. Yes. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的。好的。是的。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.32,0:29:22.36,English,,0,0,0,,So what's really important to understand is\N{\rChinese}于是要真正理解的是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.36,0:29:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,that back then, and again, I'll explain to you what I mean.\N{\rChinese}那时再回去，再次，我会把我的意思告诉你。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.28,0:29:28.14,English,,0,0,0,,I'll explain to you over the next couple of weeks.\N{\rChinese}接下来几周，我会再给你解释。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:29.62,English,,0,0,0,,Back then,\N{\rChinese}那时再回去。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.80,0:29:34.64,English,,0,0,0,,we human beings did not see us as separate from the other world.\N{\rChinese}我们人类没有把自己视为与其他世界分离。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.94,0:29:37.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? Animals, trees,\N{\rChinese}好的？这有道理吗？动物、树木、人类，皆同等。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.26,0:29:39.64,English,,0,0,0,,humans, all equal.\N{\rChinese}好的？这有道理吗？动物、树木、人类，皆同等。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.04,0:29:44.18,English,,0,0,0,,So first of all, if you're going to kill these animals,\N{\rChinese}首先，如果你要杀这些动物，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.50,0:29:47.04,English,,0,0,0,,you need to ask for their forgiveness.\N{\rChinese}你需要请求它们的赦免。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.60,0:29:51.36,English,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, their spirit, their soul will haunt you.\N{\rChinese}否则，它们的灵魂会跟随你。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:53.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They'll take revenge on you.\N{\rChinese}好的？他们会报仇。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.68,0:29:56.26,English,,0,0,0,,So if you kill these animals, you're going to get a reward.\N{\rChinese}所以如果你杀了这些动物，你会得到回报。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:59.44,English,,0,0,0,,If you kill them, you must ask for their forgiveness.\N{\rChinese}如果你杀了它们，你必须请求它们的赦免。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.78,0:30:03.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the one way to do that is by paying tribute to them.\N{\rChinese}好吧？做这件事的唯一方式就是向它们献上贡品。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.16,0:30:05.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's number one. Number two is\N{\rChinese}好的？第一点是。第二点是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.90,0:30:09.36,English,,0,0,0,,that we can learn from these animals.\N{\rChinese}我们可以从这些动物身上学到的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.48,0:30:12.08,English,,0,0,0,,Right? They're the best hunters in the world.\N{\rChinese}对吧？它们是世界上最好的猎手。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.26,0:30:13.86,English,,0,0,0,,So before we go on a hunting trip,\N{\rChinese}所以在我们去打猎之旅之前，
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:18.36,English,,0,0,0,,we might have a ceremony to channel their energy\N{\rChinese}我们可能会举行仪式来通灵它们的能量。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:20.10,English,,0,0,0,,and power and wisdom.\N{\rChinese}以及力量与智慧。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.14,0:30:23.08,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.50,0:30:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,And the third thing is basically, you know, you're going to have to be a hunter.\N{\rChinese}第三点基本上是，你知道，你将要成为猎人。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.28,0:30:29.86,English,,0,0,0,,Basically, to appease them or to become their friends.\N{\rChinese}基本上，安抚他们或成为他们的朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.36,0:30:32.08,English,,0,0,0,,Because we don't want to hunt foxes.\N{\rChinese}因为我们不想猎捕狐狸。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.10,0:30:33.38,English,,0,0,0,,We want to hunt gazelle.\N{\rChinese}我们想猎捕羚羊。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.48,0:30:35.12,English,,0,0,0,,There's more meat than gazelle. They're easier to capture.\N{\rChinese}比羚羊更有肉量，捕捉更容易。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.48,0:30:38.10,English,,0,0,0,,But we want to be friends with the gazelle.\N{\rChinese}我们想和羚羊成为朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.16,0:30:39.82,English,,0,0,0,,We want to be friends with the lion.\N{\rChinese}我们想和狮子成为朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:41.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? We don't want to be enemies.\N{\rChinese}好的？我们不想成为敌人。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.54,0:30:46.26,English,,0,0,0,,So, it's a sign of respect to the animals.\N{\rChinese}于是，向动物致敬意就是一种礼貌的标志。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.76,0:30:49.80,English,,0,0,0,,So that's basically their religion. And\N{\rChinese}于是，这基本就是他们的宗教。然后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.80,0:30:52.66,English,,0,0,0,,coming together at the religious festival was\N{\rChinese}在宗教节日聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:55.80,English,,0,0,0,,about celebrating their relationship with these animals\N{\rChinese}关于庆祝与这些动物的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.80,0:30:59.28,English,,0,0,0,,as well as channeling their power,\N{\rChinese}以及运用它们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.56,0:31:03.02,English,,0,0,0,,their energy and their wisdom so that they could go hunt as well.\N{\rChinese}他们的精力与智慧，以便能去狩猎。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.76,0:31:08.48,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So this is probably one of the earlier religions that we have.\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？这大概是我们已知的早期宗教之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.54,0:31:11.98,English,,0,0,0,,Is this clear to you guys so far?\N{\rChinese}到目前为止，你们觉得清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:15.16,English,,0,0,0,,All right. All right. Let's move on.\N{\rChinese}好的，好的。我们继续。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.68,0:31:30.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So now this is Jericho.\N{\rChinese}好的。现在这就是耶利哥。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.54,0:31:35.46,English,,0,0,0,,And Jericho is part of something called the Natufian culture.\N{\rChinese}耶利哥属于被称为纳图菲安文化的一个体系。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.14,0:31:41.96,English,,0,0,0,,And the Natufian culture appeared about 13,000 years ago or even more actually,\N{\rChinese}纳图菲安文化大约在一万三千年前出现，甚至更早。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:45.06,English,,0,0,0,,maybe 15,000 years ago in a place we call the Levant.\N{\rChinese}大约1万5千年前，在我们称之为黎凡特的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.24,0:31:48.88,English,,0,0,0,,The Levant is basically the Middle East, Israel and Syria.\N{\rChinese}黎凡特基本上就是中东、以色列和叙利亚。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.56,0:31:53.44,English,,0,0,0,,And what was special about the Natufian culture are three things.\N{\rChinese}纳图菲安文化的三大特色是：
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.48,0:31:58.20,English,,0,0,0,,First. First of all, they were sedentary.\N{\rChinese}首先，第一点，他们是定居的。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.76,0:32:03.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Sedentary basically means that\N{\rChinese}好的。定居基本上是指他们……
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:07.84,English,,0,0,0,,they basically stayed in one place.\N{\rChinese}好的。他们基本上停留在同一地点。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.00,0:32:09.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Remember, hunter -gatherers, they roamed around.\N{\rChinese}好的。记住，狩猎采集者，他们四处游走。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.04,0:32:13.84,English,,0,0,0,,They moved from place to place. But\N{\rChinese}他们从一个地方搬到另一个地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.84,0:32:16.32,English,,0,0,0,,they were hunter -gatherers who were sanitary.\N{\rChinese}他们是四处游走的狩猎采集者。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.56,0:32:18.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. They were not farmers.\N{\rChinese}好的。他们不是农民。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.94,0:32:20.68,English,,0,0,0,,They were hunter -gatherers. But they stayed in one place.\N{\rChinese}他们是狩猎采集者，但他们定居在同一地点。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.32,0:32:23.86,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why we know, there's a lot of evidence, but\N{\rChinese}我们知道的原因有很多证据。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:27.74,English,,0,0,0,,one reason why we know is that they basically hunted gazelles.\N{\rChinese}一个原因是他们基本上是猎捕角马的。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.92,0:32:30.00,English,,0,0,0,,Gazelles are like deers, right? And\N{\rChinese}角马像鹿一样，对吧？而且
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.00,0:32:34.94,English,,0,0,0,,the thing about gazelles is their teeth color is different according to the season.\N{\rChinese}角马的牙色随季节变化。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.26,0:32:38.84,English,,0,0,0,,So in the summer and in the winter, because they eat different foods.\N{\rChinese}于是夏季和冬季，他们吃不同的食物。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.96,0:32:40.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So the teeth color is different.\N{\rChinese}好的，所以牙色不同。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:45.68,English,,0,0,0,,So we're able to dig up these gazelle bones, look at the teeth and recognize that, oh,\N{\rChinese}于是我们可以挖出这些角马骨头，观察牙齿并认出它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:50.84,English,,0,0,0,,they were hunting gazelle in this area both in the summer\N{\rChinese}他们在这个地区夏季也在狩猎角马。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.84,0:32:52.48,English,,0,0,0,,and the winter, which meant they did not move.\N{\rChinese}在冬季，他们也不迁徙。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.62,0:32:54.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So they were sedentary.\N{\rChinese}好的。所以他们是定居的。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.40,0:32:55.88,English,,0,0,0,,That's the first thing.\N{\rChinese}第一点是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.38,0:33:00.48,English,,0,0,0,,Second thing is that they had domesticated crops.\N{\rChinese}第二点是他们已经驯化了农作物。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.86,0:33:07.74,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why we know is we're able to dig up seeds of crops.\N{\rChinese}于是我们能挖出作物种子，知道它们的存在。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.98,0:33:10.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Vegetables and wheat and\N{\rChinese}好了。蔬菜、麦子等作物。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.68,0:33:13.42,English,,0,0,0,,barley, which meant that they had the capacity,\N{\rChinese}大麦，这意味着他们具备种植的能力，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:16.94,English,,0,0,0,,the technology to farm, but they chose not to farm.\N{\rChinese}但他们选择不去种植。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.28,0:33:18.64,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:22.36,English,,0,0,0,,So basically, the way they developed this technology is for gardening.\N{\rChinese}基本上，他们发展这项技术的方式就是种菜。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.84,0:33:24.38,English,,0,0,0,,Right. They were hunting -gathering.\N{\rChinese}对了。他们是狩猎采集。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.38,0:33:28.42,English,,0,0,0,,They were hunting -gathering most of the time. But some of them, for fun, for pleasure, had their own garden.\N{\rChinese}他们大部分时间是狩猎采集。但有些人，出于乐趣，自己种了花园。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:30.36,English,,0,0,0,,And that's how they developed the technology.\N{\rChinese}于是他们就这样发展了技术。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.96,0:33:34.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. And the third thing\N{\rChinese}好的，第三点是……
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.84,0:33:36.04,English,,0,0,0,,that\N{\rChinese}那点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.04,0:33:38.64,English,,0,0,0,,was very important is they had something\N{\rChinese}很重要的是他们有个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:42.04,English,,0,0,0,,called the cult of the skull.\N{\rChinese}叫做“头骨崇拜”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.26,0:33:45.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So\N{\rChinese}好的。于是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.54,0:33:49.58,English,,0,0,0,,they probably worshipped animals,\N{\rChinese}他们大概会崇拜动物，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.82,0:33:52.46,English,,0,0,0,,but they also worshipped ancestors.\N{\rChinese}他们也会崇拜祖先。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:55.14,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why we think so is because they worshipped animals. Right.\N{\rChinese}并且我们之所以这么认为，是因为他们崇拜动物。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.60,0:34:02.22,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.22,0:34:05.12,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right. Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.12,0:34:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.72,0:34:12.38,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right. Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.64,0:34:14.46,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.46,0:34:17.15,English,,0,0,0,,Right. Right.\N{\rChinese}对。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.76,0:34:22.20,English,,0,0,0,,Right. and it's called the Tower of Jericho.\N{\rChinese}对。并且它叫作耶利米塔楼。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.74,0:34:25.28,English,,0,0,0,,When we first discovered this, we thought, oh,\N{\rChinese}当我们第一次发现它时，我们想，哦，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.42,0:34:30.14,English,,0,0,0,,this must be a evidence\N{\rChinese}这必须是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.10,0:34:34.40,English,,0,0,0,,that Jericho went to war, okay?\N{\rChinese}耶利米塔城曾经战争，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:36.66,English,,0,0,0,,Because it had walls and it had a tower, right?\N{\rChinese}因为它有墙和塔，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.52,English,,0,0,0,,The walls are to protect you from your enemies.\N{\rChinese}墙是用来保护你免受敌人之害。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:41.96,English,,0,0,0,,The tower is to see your enemies coming.\N{\rChinese}塔是用来观察敌人来临。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.96,0:34:46.04,English,,0,0,0,,But then they did more research and realized that, oh, no,\N{\rChinese}但随后他们做了更多研究，才发现，哦，没错。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.16,0:34:50.16,English,,0,0,0,,no, no, this tower is a religious monument.\N{\rChinese}不不，这座塔是宗教纪念碑。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.52,0:34:54.50,English,,0,0,0,,It is the same as Gobletepe where it is cosmological,\N{\rChinese}它与戈布莱特佩一样，具有宇宙学意义，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:59.62,English,,0,0,0,,meaning that at the longest day of the year,\N{\rChinese}即在一年中最长的一天，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.58,0:35:04.94,English,,0,0,0,,the mountain over here will cast\N{\rChinese}这里的山会投下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.94,0:35:07.90,English,,0,0,0,,a shadow over the tower.\N{\rChinese}塔上投下阴影。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.16,0:35:10.70,English,,0,0,0,,The tower will cast a shadow over the entire village,\N{\rChinese}塔会把阴影投到整个村庄。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.24,0:35:13.68,English,,0,0,0,,covering it all up in darkness.\N{\rChinese}把它全部覆盖在黑暗里。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.16,0:35:17.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense, you guys?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗，你们？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.78,0:35:19.22,English,,0,0,0,,Why would they wanna do that?\N{\rChinese}他们为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.24,0:35:21.80,English,,0,0,0,,What does that do for you?\N{\rChinese}这对你有什么好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.02,0:35:23.84,English,,0,0,0,,To have the entire village cover up in darkness?\N{\rChinese}让整个村庄全被黑暗覆盖？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:31.76,English,,0,0,0,,Any guesses? Why would they do that?\N{\rChinese}有什么猜测吗？他们为什么这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.18,0:35:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? What do you mean by that?\N{\rChinese}请问？你这句话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.94,0:35:47.46,English,,0,0,0,,..!\N{\rChinese}……！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.64,0:35:50.60,English,,0,0,0,,. I know,\N{\rChinese}我知道，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.68,0:35:52.60,English,,0,0,0,,but if that were the case, you'd just move, right?\N{\rChinese}但如果是那样，你就会搬过去，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.88,0:35:55.72,English,,0,0,0,,So, okay, so what's really important is that\N{\rChinese}所以，好的，最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.72,0:35:58.74,English,,0,0,0,,this is like right after the last ice age, okay?\N{\rChinese}这就像是刚好在上一次冰河之后，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.92,0:36:00.22,English,,0,0,0,,So it's actually pretty cold.\N{\rChinese}所以实际上挺冷的。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.28,0:36:03.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They did this for religious reasons, right?\N{\rChinese}好吧？他们这么做是出于宗教原因，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.18,0:36:07.68,English,,0,0,0,,Because when you cover your village in darkness, you feel as\N{\rChinese}因为当你把村庄覆上黑暗时，你会觉得自己与天空相连。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:11.88,English,,0,0,0,,though you are in connection with the sky.\N{\rChinese}就像你与天空相连一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.38,0:36:14.96,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So they must have a religious belief.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？所以他们一定有宗教信仰。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.96,0:36:19.44,English,,0,0,0,,They must have a religious belief in which part of the worship is to cover the village in darkness.\N{\rChinese}他们的宗教信仰中，祭祀的一部分就是把村庄覆上黑暗。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.00,English,,0,0,0,,..\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.00,0:36:25.10,English,,0,0,0,,..\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.10,0:36:26.54,English,,0,0,0,,.......\N{\rChinese}……
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.10,0:36:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,...\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.08,0:36:31.92,English,,0,0,0,,..\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.92,0:36:40.44,English,,0,0,0,,. This makes\N{\rChinese}这有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:48.56,English,,0,0,0,,sense. This\N{\rChinese}意思。此
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.56,0:36:59.98,English,,0,0,0,,makes sense.\N{\rChinese}此有道理。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.54,0:37:01.94,English,,0,0,0,,This makes sense.\N{\rChinese}此有道理。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.96,0:37:04.92,English,,0,0,0,,Okay So they design a tower in a certain way\N{\rChinese}好的，所以他们以某种方式设计了塔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,So that it would cover the village in darkness\N{\rChinese}以便让它把村庄覆盖在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.46,0:37:11.62,English,,0,0,0,,and they could see that as magic and that's evidence\N{\rChinese}于是他们把这看作魔法，便成了证据
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.62,0:37:14.44,English,,0,0,0,,that your religion is correct Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}那你的宗教是正确的，这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:19.00,English,,0,0,0,,Right these otherwise, how do you know your religion is correct?\N{\rChinese}好吧，除此之外，你怎么知道你的宗教是正确的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.98,0:37:21.46,English,,0,0,0,,Only by performing magic.\N{\rChinese}只有通过施展魔法。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.56,0:37:24.06,English,,0,0,0,,Can you show that this charismatic leader?\N{\rChinese}你能展示这位有魅力的领袖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.44,0:37:25.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, who came up this idea?\N{\rChinese}好的，谁提出了这个想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.20,0:37:29.94,English,,0,0,0,,It speaks to God Okay, does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}它向上帝说话，好的，这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.02,0:37:34.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so let's look at sort of pictures of skulls.\N{\rChinese}好的，让我们先看看几张骷髅的图片。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.84,0:37:37.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, because this was actually very common back then\N{\rChinese}好的，因为那时这件事其实很常见。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.46,0:37:45.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so basically this is a skull they covered up with clay\N{\rChinese}基本上这是一块被粘土覆盖的骷髅。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.70,0:37:50.04,English,,0,0,0,,and they carried around with them all over the place and this Is true throughout the world at that time.\N{\rChinese}并且他们把它们随身携带到各处，这在当时的世界各地都是真实的。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.12,0:37:54.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, and just answer worship Okay\N{\rChinese}好的，接着回答敬拜吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.28,0:38:05.76,English,,0,0,0,,So this is another picture of the skull\N{\rChinese}这又是一张骷髅的图片。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.72,0:38:10.34,English,,0,0,0,,Skull okay. Let me ask you why they would do that\N{\rChinese}骷髅，好吗？让我问问他们为什么会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.06,0:38:13.98,English,,0,0,0,,Their ancestors dead. Why would they do that?\N{\rChinese}他们的祖先已逝。为什么他们会这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.02,0:38:15.02,English,,0,0,0,,Why would they have to skull around?\N{\rChinese}他们为什么要把骷髅带在身边？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.94,0:38:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,Where's the ancestors now?\N{\rChinese}祖先现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.18,0:38:31.44,English,,0,0,0,,Where's the dead person? Where's the dead person?\N{\rChinese}死者在哪里？死者在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.40,0:38:35.70,English,,0,0,0,,The spirit ward right someplace in another world\N{\rChinese}灵魂守护在另一个世界的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.70,0:38:38.72,English,,0,0,0,,and therefore having a skull around allows you to communicate with\N{\rChinese}并且拥有一个骷髅在身边可以让你与之沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.72,0:38:40.58,English,,0,0,0,,that world and learn its secrets\N{\rChinese}那世界并且能让你领悟其奥秘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.66,0:38:43.56,English,,0,0,0,,You understand and\N{\rChinese}你已明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.56,0:38:47.70,English,,0,0,0,,some of the secrets may be like how to construct a tower in a way\N{\rChinese}一些秘密可能像是怎样以某种方式建造塔楼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.46,0:38:51.68,English,,0,0,0,,That you're able to cast a shadow over the village\N{\rChinese}你能把影子投在村子上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.50,0:38:56.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so that's their method But then we also have the idea of scientific discovery\N{\rChinese}好的，那就是他们的方法，但我们也有科学发现的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.52,0:39:01.16,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense to communicate with the spirit world through for your ancestors?\N{\rChinese}这有意义吗？通过它与祖先的灵界沟通？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.18,0:39:06.96,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay, the point I'm going to tell you is that\N{\rChinese}这有意义吗？好了，我要说的重点是……
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.82,0:39:11.96,English,,0,0,0,,Their level of intelligence or their understand the world.\N{\rChinese}他们的智力水平或对世界的理解。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.06,0:39:14.50,English,,0,0,0,,It's just as sophisticated as artists in the world.\N{\rChinese}它就像世界里的艺术家一样精巧。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.60,0:39:17.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay There's that we think\N{\rChinese}好的，我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.82,0:39:20.88,English,,0,0,0,,that when we go to science class we're learning facts and\N{\rChinese}当我们去上科学课时，我们在学事实
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.92,0:39:23.62,English,,0,0,0,,Knowledge but guess what?\N{\rChinese}知识，但你猜怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.68,0:39:26.52,English,,0,0,0,,Maybe a thousand years from now? people will look at our science,\N{\rChinese}大约一千年后？人们会看我们的科学，像物理学，然后说，哦，那也是一种宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.54,0:39:28.56,English,,0,0,0,,like the physics, and be like, oh, that was a religion too.\N{\rChinese}like the physics, and be like, oh, that was a religion too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.96,0:39:32.26,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So, in terms of intelligence,\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？从智力上说，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.66,0:39:36.08,English,,0,0,0,,they were just as creative and as sophisticated as we are today,\N{\rChinese}他们和我们今天一样有创造力和精巧，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.30,0:39:37.86,English,,0,0,0,,but they just had a different set of beliefs.\N{\rChinese}只是他们的信仰体系不同。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.62,0:39:44.46,English,,0,0,0,,Alright, so the last place I want to look at is Kanahoyak, okay? So Kanahoyak,\N{\rChinese}好的，接下来我想看的地方是卡纳霍亚克，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.92,0:39:57.96,English,,0,0,0,,Kanahoyak is a huge place, okay, in Turkey as well,\N{\rChinese}卡纳霍亚克是一个很大的地方，好吗，位于土耳其也，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.84,0:40:03.54,English,,0,0,0,,pretty far from Gopalantepe, but about the same place.\N{\rChinese}它离戈帕兰特佩相当远，但大致在同一地区。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.68,0:40:06.24,English,,0,0,0,,And this dates back about 7500 BCE.\N{\rChinese}它的年代约在公元前7500年。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:11.56,English,,0,0,0,,And as you can see, it's a huge village.\N{\rChinese}正如你所见，它是一个大村落。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:15.22,English,,0,0,0,,And we think that, at its height, okay,\N{\rChinese}我们认为，在它的鼎盛时期，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:20.00,English,,0,0,0,,maybe this was around for about 2,000 years, but at its height of development, of civilization,\N{\rChinese}也许它存在了大约两千年，但在鼎盛时期，文明发展到极点时，约有八千人。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.60,0:40:22.44,English,,0,0,0,,it had about 8,000 people.\N{\rChinese}大约八千人。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.82,0:40:24.54,English,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of people, guys, okay?\N{\rChinese}这可是很多人，大家好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:29.00,English,,0,0,0,,And the thing about Kanahoyak\N{\rChinese}以及关于卡纳霍亚克的事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.00,0:40:33.08,English,,0,0,0,,that stands out is, first of all, it's huge, okay?\N{\rChinese}首先，它很大，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:34.76,English,,0,0,0,,Second of all,\N{\rChinese}其次，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.56,0:40:42.96,English,,0,0,0,,they didn't have a place of worship or government,\N{\rChinese}他们没有专门的祭祀或政府场所，好的？意思是所有房屋都一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.16,0:40:46.44,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Meaning that all the houses were the same.\N{\rChinese}它是一个非常平等的社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:48.98,English,,0,0,0,,It was a very egalitarian society.\N{\rChinese}It was a very egalitarian society.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.40,0:40:53.12,English,,0,0,0,,Everyone was the same. And what's even more interesting is\N{\rChinese}人人都一样。更有趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.12,0:40:55.36,English,,0,0,0,,that if you go to every house,\N{\rChinese}如果你去每间房子，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.84,0:41:00.26,English,,0,0,0,,there's a site, the living room is basically a temple unto itself.\N{\rChinese}有一个地方，客厅基本就是自己的寺庙。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:05.10,English,,0,0,0,,It was a place of worship and religion, okay?\N{\rChinese}它是一个祭祀与宗教的场所，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.44,0:41:07.90,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that the first,\N{\rChinese}意思是最初的，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.02,0:41:11.18,English,,0,0,0,,like, Kanahoyak is a place where\N{\rChinese}像，Kanahoyak是一个场所
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.18,0:41:13.34,English,,0,0,0,,religion permeated, okay, the temple.\N{\rChinese}宗教渗透进了，好的，寺庙。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.34,0:41:15.48,English,,0,0,0,,It was in every place.\N{\rChinese}它存在于每一个地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:19.28,English,,0,0,0,,They were, okay? So we think\N{\rChinese}他们是这样，好的？所以我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.28,0:41:23.08,English,,0,0,0,,that Kanahoyak is one of the first religious communities.\N{\rChinese}那是Kanahoyak是最早的宗教社群之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.18,0:41:29.96,English,,0,0,0,,Remember that before, religious sites or places you went to,\N{\rChinese}记得以前，宗教场所或你去过的地方，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:32.98,English,,0,0,0,,maybe once in your lifetime or maybe once a year, okay?\N{\rChinese}可能一辈子一次，或者一年一次，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.16,0:41:35.34,English,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't part of your everyday life.\N{\rChinese}但它并不是你日常生活的一部分。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.60,0:41:37.10,English,,0,0,0,,Whereas in Kanahoyak,\N{\rChinese}而在Kanahoyak，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:42.14,English,,0,0,0,,religion was in your life from birth to death,\N{\rChinese}宗教从出生到死亡贯穿你的生活。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.36,0:41:43.84,English,,0,0,0,,okay? So, you know, it's a very, very, very, very, very, okay, okay. Does that makes sense.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，你知道，真是非常非常非常非常非常好，好的，好的。这样说通吗。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.40,0:41:49.24,English,,0,0,0,,And the think about Kanahoyak that's very interesting is at this point,\N{\rChinese}而且关于Kanahoyak的想法，最有趣味的就是此时，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.44,English,,0,0,0,,their religion is extremely sophisticated.\N{\rChinese}他们的宗教极为精巧。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.78,0:41:55.88,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that they can explain everything using their religion.\N{\rChinese}意思是他们可以用宗教来解释一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.14,0:41:59.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So their everyday life\N{\rChinese}好的。所以他们的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.46,0:42:02.68,English,,0,0,0,,and their religion was completely aligned together.\N{\rChinese}以及他们的宗教完全一致。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.18,0:42:05.26,English,,0,0,0,,So let me show you some evidence of this.\N{\rChinese}好了，我来给你展示一些证据。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.42,0:42:15.82,English,,0,0,0,,So this is a painting that\N{\rChinese}这是一幅画，画中……
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.82,0:42:20.38,English,,0,0,0,,you will see in every house or most houses in Kanahoye.\N{\rChinese}你会在卡纳霍耶的每一所房子里看到它。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.48,0:42:22.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right?\N{\rChinese}好的？行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.62,0:42:27.00,English,,0,0,0,,So you're like, what is going on here?\N{\rChinese}那你说，事情怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.04,0:42:31.10,English,,0,0,0,,So again, there are different theories.\N{\rChinese}再说一次，理论各不相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.40,0:42:36.38,English,,0,0,0,,But let me explain to you what most scholars believe to be the accurate theories.\N{\rChinese}但让我来解释一下大多数学者认为最准确的理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.54,0:42:37.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So this is just a theory.\N{\rChinese}好？这只是一个理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.04,0:42:39.36,English,,0,0,0,,We have no evidence for this.\N{\rChinese}我们没有证据支持这一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.52,0:42:42.62,English,,0,0,0,,But this is what we believe. We believe\N{\rChinese}但这就是我们的信念。我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.62,0:42:44.86,English,,0,0,0,,that the people at Kanahoye,\N{\rChinese}在卡纳霍耶的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:48.12,English,,0,0,0,,they worship a mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}他们崇拜母神。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.92,0:42:52.18,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because a mother goddess is what gives life to everything.\N{\rChinese}好的？因为母神是赋予万物生命的存在。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.34,0:42:53.96,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Think of Mother Nature.\N{\rChinese}对吧？想想大自然母亲。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.68,0:42:57.56,English,,0,0,0,,Think of a woman giving birth to a child.\N{\rChinese}想想一个女人生下孩子的情景。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.68,0:42:59.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So they worship a mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}好的？于是他们崇拜母神。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.14,0:43:03.64,English,,0,0,0,,And the mother goddess is represented by the bird.\N{\rChinese}而母神则以鸟的形象出现。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.82,0:43:06.10,English,,0,0,0,,Because the bird flies all around the sky.\N{\rChinese}因为鸟在天空中自由飞翔。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.22,0:43:08.90,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So the sky belongs to the bird.\N{\rChinese}对吧？于是天空归鸟所有。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.78,0:43:12.36,English,,0,0,0,,Now, what is the mother goddess? Now, the bird can take different forms.\N{\rChinese}现在，母神是什么？现在，鸟可以变成不同的形态。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.72,0:43:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,This is a vulture. Right?\N{\rChinese}这是一只秃鹰。对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:18.32,English,,0,0,0,,So the mother goddess can also take the form of a vulture.\N{\rChinese}于是母神也能化作秃鹰。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.58,0:43:20.70,English,,0,0,0,,So what's going on here?\N{\rChinese}那到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.92,0:43:26.72,English,,0,0,0,,Why is the vulture with headless people?\N{\rChinese}为什么秃鹰会跟无头人一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.08,0:43:30.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because the way that\N{\rChinese}好的？因为他们把祖先崇拜和对母神的信仰结合起来，认为当…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.66,0:43:35.40,English,,0,0,0,,they combine ancestral worship with their belief\N{\rChinese}他们把祖先崇拜与对母神的信仰结合起来，认为当…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.40,0:43:38.16,English,,0,0,0,,in the mother goddess is they believe that when\N{\rChinese}他们把祖先崇拜与对母神的信仰结合起来，认为当…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.16,0:43:40.62,English,,0,0,0,,a person dies, what they'll do is they'll die.\N{\rChinese}一个人去世后，他们会把他放在外面。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.62,0:43:44.26,English,,0,0,0,,They'll put that person's dead body out in the open.\N{\rChinese}他们会把那个人的尸体摆在外面。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.38,0:43:45.74,English,,0,0,0,,It's a sky burial. Right?\N{\rChinese}这是一种天葬。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.92,0:43:47.64,English,,0,0,0,,You go to Tibet, they have sky burials.\N{\rChinese}你去西藏，他们有天葬。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.10,0:43:50.30,English,,0,0,0,,The vultures will come and eat all the flesh.\N{\rChinese}秃鹰会来吃掉全肉。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.48,0:43:55.22,English,,0,0,0,,And that is the tribute or the sacrifice made to the mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}这就是向母神献祭的礼物。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.48,0:43:58.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So the mother goddess basically cleans the body.\N{\rChinese}好的？于是母神基本把尸体清理干净。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.88,0:44:02.30,English,,0,0,0,,And then you take the bones and you bury it back in your house.\N{\rChinese}然后你把骨头取出来，再把它们埋回你家里。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.92,0:44:05.28,English,,0,0,0,,And you take the skull and\N{\rChinese}你把头骨取出来并……
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.28,0:44:08.72,English,,0,0,0,,you keep the skull in your living room to worship your ancestors.\N{\rChinese}你把头骨放在客厅里祭拜祖先。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.72,0:44:10.44,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}这样说对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.92,0:44:12.16,English,,0,0,0,,So in other words,\N{\rChinese}换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.44,0:44:18.38,English,,0,0,0,,it is an extremely comprehensive or complete religion,\N{\rChinese}它是一种极其全面或完整的宗教，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.58,0:44:21.36,English,,0,0,0,,understanding the world. Okay?\N{\rChinese}理解世界。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.56,0:44:23.92,English,,0,0,0,,Is that clear to you guys? What the religion is?\N{\rChinese}这宗教是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.28,0:44:25.50,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions so far?\N{\rChinese}到目前为止还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.68,0:44:27.86,English,,0,0,0,,Again, by the way guys, a theory.\N{\rChinese}再说一句，顺便说一句，大家，理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.02,0:44:30.92,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But right now, the most useful theory\N{\rChinese}好的？但现在，最有用的理论是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.92,0:44:32.82,English,,0,0,0,,that we have about this place.\N{\rChinese}我们对这个地方的了解。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.26,0:44:35.10,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions before I move on?\N{\rChinese}我继续之前还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:38.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So.\N{\rChinese}好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.68,0:44:49.32,English,,0,0,0,,So what's going on here? Okay?\N{\rChinese}那么这里发生了什么？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.74,0:44:54.28,English,,0,0,0,,Now, this again also is in Kadahoyak, many houses.\N{\rChinese}现在，这又在卡达霍亚克出现，很多房子。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.14,0:44:57.16,English,,0,0,0,,So what's going on here? Okay.\N{\rChinese}那么这里发生了什么？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.24,0:45:00.34,English,,0,0,0,,So different scholars have different interpretations of this.\N{\rChinese}所以不同的学者对这件事有不同的解释。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.44,0:45:03.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Clearly, this is a hunt.\N{\rChinese}好吧？显然，这是一场狩猎。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.82,0:45:05.74,English,,0,0,0,,Right? This is a hunt.\N{\rChinese}对吧？这是一场狩猎。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.04,0:45:09.08,English,,0,0,0,,And. And some people believe that\N{\rChinese}而且，有些人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.08,0:45:12.16,English,,0,0,0,,these human beings who\N{\rChinese}这些人类，正是卡达霍亚克人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.16,0:45:15.08,English,,0,0,0,,are, you know, part of the Kadahoyak people,\N{\rChinese}are, you know, part ofthe Kadahoyak people,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:18.94,English,,0,0,0,,they are mocking or taunting or\N{\rChinese}他们在嘲笑或挑衅或笑着对动物进行戏弄，以此来驯服它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.94,0:45:23.74,English,,0,0,0,,laughing at the animals as a way to subdue them, to tame them.\N{\rChinese}他们在嘲笑或挑衅或笑着对动物进行戏弄，以此来驯服它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.84,0:45:25.22,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? To domesticate them.\N{\rChinese}好的？让它们驯养。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.32,0:45:29.30,English,,0,0,0,,That's one theory. But another theory is that\N{\rChinese}这是一种理论。但另一种理论是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.30,0:45:32.30,English,,0,0,0,,what they're really doing is dancing\N{\rChinese}他们真正做的事是舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.30,0:45:33.58,English,,0,0,0,,because\N{\rChinese}因为
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.58,0:45:38.80,English,,0,0,0,,they are worshipping or paying tribute to these animals they are about to kill.\N{\rChinese}他们在祭拜或向即将要杀的动物献祭。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.08,0:45:43.58,English,,0,0,0,,Or they are trying. So, let's go back to Kobayatepe.\N{\rChinese}或者他们在尝试。好了，回到小巴亚特佩去。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.94,0:45:46.64,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Where they're trying to respect the animals.\N{\rChinese}对吧？他们正试着尊敬这些动物。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.00,0:45:48.26,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Dance with you.\N{\rChinese}对吧？跟你一起舞蹈。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.30,0:45:50.50,English,,0,0,0,,We're friends. I'm sorry I have to kill you.\N{\rChinese}我们是朋友。我很抱歉要杀了你。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.66,0:45:52.48,English,,0,0,0,,But, hey, we're only taking your meat.\N{\rChinese}不过，嘿，我们只是拿你的肉。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.60,0:45:54.90,English,,0,0,0,,Your soul. Right?\N{\rChinese}你的灵魂。对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.02,0:45:57.08,English,,0,0,0,,Is still going to be reborn.\N{\rChinese}它仍将重生。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.50,0:46:00.04,English,,0,0,0,,Or it's going to go to the spirit world.\N{\rChinese}或者它将去往灵界。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.20,0:46:01.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好的？那么，
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:05.36,English,,0,0,0,,this is a way of paying tribute or respecting the animals.\N{\rChinese}这是一种向动物致敬或敬畜的方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.32,0:46:08.18,English,,0,0,0,,They're about to kill or about to hunt.\N{\rChinese}他们正要杀戮或狩猎。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.82,0:46:12.36,English,,0,0,0,,To maintain the harmony of nature\N{\rChinese}保持自然的和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.36,0:46:14.02,English,,0,0,0,,and their relationship with nature.\N{\rChinese}以及他们与自然的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.40,0:46:17.12,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense, guys? Okay?\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗，大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.50,0:46:20.60,English,,0,0,0,,Again, what's really important is that\N{\rChinese}再次，真正重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.60,0:46:22.86,English,,0,0,0,,this is a pretty complete religion.\N{\rChinese}这是一套相当完整的宗教体系。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.04,0:46:26.04,English,,0,0,0,,Right? That explains everything to these people.\N{\rChinese}对吧？这就解释了这些人所需的一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:28.38,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why it's so attractive to people.\N{\rChinese}于是这才是人们如此钟爱的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.50,0:46:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,Right? If you're a human being, you like, you want to know why.\N{\rChinese}对吧？如果你是人类，你会想知道原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.90,0:46:35.34,English,,0,0,0,,Well, Kadahoyak, the religion there, explains everything.\N{\rChinese}好吧，Kadahoyak那里的宗教解释了一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.36,0:46:37.68,English,,0,0,0,,It explains why. Okay?\N{\rChinese}它解释了原因。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.76,0:46:40.20,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense so far? Any more, any questions?\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？还有什么？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.46,0:46:52.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So, this is a picture of the mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}好了。于是这是一幅母神的图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.78,0:46:56.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Again, we have, we have debate about what this is.\N{\rChinese}好的？再说一次，我们有关于这是什么的争论。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.46,0:46:59.04,English,,0,0,0,,Some people believe that it's just a fertility goddess.\N{\rChinese}有些人认为它只是一个生育女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.88,0:47:02.00,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But others believe this is the mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}好的？但也有人认为这是母神。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.12,0:47:04.36,English,,0,0,0,,And you think about it.\N{\rChinese}于是你会想到它。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.28,0:47:09.04,English,,0,0,0,,If you are a place like Kadahoyak,\N{\rChinese}如果你是像Kadahoyak这样的地方，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.28,0:47:12.34,English,,0,0,0,,you're most concerned about giving birth.\N{\rChinese}你最关心的是生育。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.52,0:47:16.24,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Because giving birth is what rejuvenates your society.\N{\rChinese}对吧？因为生育是让社会焕发活力的根源。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.02,0:47:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,So, it makes sense that your god,\N{\rChinese}于是，你的神，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.98,0:47:22.16,English,,0,0,0,,the person you worship the most, would be a mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}你最敬拜的那位神，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:24.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.30,0:47:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,This is clearly a bull.\N{\rChinese}这明显是一头公牛。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.04,0:47:34.34,English,,0,0,0,,And if you see pictures of Kadahoyak, you realize that it's a mother goddess.\N{\rChinese}如果你看到Kadahoyak的图像，你会意识到它是母神。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.34,0:47:36.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And you will see that they have many,\N{\rChinese}好的？你会看到他们有很多，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.28,0:47:40.98,English,,0,0,0,,many depictions or pictures of bull in their house.\N{\rChinese}很多在他们的房子里出现的公牛图像或照片。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.14,0:47:43.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And what we believe, again, this is a theory.\N{\rChinese}好的？我们再次相信，这只是一个理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.94,0:47:46.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? What we believe is that\N{\rChinese}好的吗？我们认为是这样：
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.88,0:47:51.02,English,,0,0,0,,if the mother goddess represents life,\N{\rChinese}如果母神代表生命，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.24,0:47:56.74,English,,0,0,0,,okay, giving life, the bull represents vitality energy.\N{\rChinese}好的，赋予生命，公牛代表活力能量。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.32,0:47:59.36,English,,0,0,0,,And so, it's the bull that\N{\rChinese}于是，正是那头公牛给母神注入生育之力。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.36,0:48:02.80,English,,0,0,0,,gives the mother goddess the energy to give birth.\N{\rChinese}给母神注入生育之力。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.64,0:48:05.08,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}对吗？听得通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.54,0:48:08.40,English,,0,0,0,,So, the bull represents the male.\N{\rChinese}于是，公牛代表男性。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.78,0:48:10.44,English,,0,0,0,,The mother goddess represents the female.\N{\rChinese}母神代表女性。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.58,0:48:13.76,English,,0,0,0,,But only if the male and the female conjoin, they come together,\N{\rChinese}但只有当男性和女性结合时，他们才会在一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.12,0:48:15.88,English,,0,0,0,,will you have life.\N{\rChinese}你将拥有生命。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.86,0:48:18.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, this is another picture.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，这又是一幅画。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.08,0:48:20.48,English,,0,0,0,,Clearly, okay, they're not hunting.\N{\rChinese}显然，好的，他们不是在狩猎。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.58,0:48:23.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Clearly, they are worshiping the bull.\N{\rChinese}好的？显然，他们在崇拜公牛。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.76,0:48:26.44,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? They're paying tribute to the bull.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？他们在向公牛献祭。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.94,0:48:33.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.58,0:48:35.76,English,,0,0,0,,are we clear about this?\N{\rChinese}我们对此清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.12,0:48:41.24,English,,0,0,0,,How religion was a fundamental part of people's existence\N{\rChinese}宗教是人们存在的根本部分
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.24,0:48:44.70,English,,0,0,0,,when they chose to become sanitary.\N{\rChinese}当他们决定变得卫生时
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.94,0:48:46.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Or they chose to settle in one place.\N{\rChinese}好的吗？或者他们选择在一个地方定居。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.10,0:48:50.34,English,,0,0,0,,So, let's go back to the original question.\N{\rChinese}那么，让我们回到最初的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.50,0:48:52.54,English,,0,0,0,,And I'll take questions. The original question is,\N{\rChinese}我来回答问题。最初的问题是，
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.74,0:48:57.32,English,,0,0,0,,why did people transition into agriculture?\N{\rChinese}为什么人们会转向农业？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.32,0:49:01.72,English,,0,0,0,,And the theory that most scholars believe is because of religion.\N{\rChinese}而大多数学者认为的理论是因为宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.94,0:49:04.70,English,,0,0,0,,It was because people had a religious need\N{\rChinese}因为人们有宗教需求。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.70,0:49:07.36,English,,0,0,0,,that they came together to have these religious festivals.\N{\rChinese}他们聚在一起，举行这些宗教节日。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.76,0:49:11.00,English,,0,0,0,,There were some charismatic leaders who were\N{\rChinese}有些有魅力的领袖，十分出众，大家便跟随他们定居。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.00,0:49:15.54,English,,0,0,0,,so brilliant that people chose to settle down with them.\N{\rChinese}so brilliant that people chose to settle down with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.90,0:49:18.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And so, they became sanitary.\N{\rChinese}好的？于是他们变得干净。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.82,0:49:22.06,English,,0,0,0,,They developed a religion around the sanitary lifestyle,\N{\rChinese}他们围绕清洁生活方式发展了一种宗教，包括祖先崇拜。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.32,0:49:24.70,English,,0,0,0,,which included ancestor worship.\N{\rChinese}which included ancestor worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.70,0:49:27.44,English,,0,0,0,,But over time, because\N{\rChinese}但随着时间的推移，因为你停留在同一处，你会耗尽周边资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.44,0:49:33.26,English,,0,0,0,,you're in one place, you're going to deplete the resources of the area around you,\N{\rChinese}于是你会把宗教带到新地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.34,0:49:36.94,English,,0,0,0,,right? Of the forest. Which means that you must go to farming.\N{\rChinese}对吧？来自森林的那点意思是你必须去耕种。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.78,0:49:40.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? So,\N{\rChinese}好吧？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.64,0:49:43.90,English,,0,0,0,,but then eventually, because you have so much population\N{\rChinese}但随后，随着人口的增加
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.90,0:49:47.36,English,,0,0,0,,and you farm too much, you're forced to move somewhere else.\N{\rChinese}以及耕种的扩张，你被迫迁移到别处
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.52,0:49:51.28,English,,0,0,0,,And when you move somewhere else, you actually bring your religion with you.\N{\rChinese}当你迁移到别处时，你会把宗教带过去。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.40,0:49:54.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And that's how we can explain the culture.\N{\rChinese}好吧？这就是我们解释文化的方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.70,0:49:58.02,English,,0,0,0,,And that's how we can explain the transition from hunter -gatherer to agriculture.\N{\rChinese}于是我们就能解释从狩猎采集到农业的转变。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:50:03.54,English,,0,0,0,,And there was no one spark or one moment when this happened.\N{\rChinese}并且没有哪一瞬间或哪一火花促成此变。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.66,0:50:06.16,English,,0,0,0,,We think it took thousands of years over time.\N{\rChinese}我们认为这需要数千年的时间。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.40,0:50:08.32,English,,0,0,0,,Because ultimately,\N{\rChinese}因为最终，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.68,0:50:11.48,English,,0,0,0,,the hunter -gatherer lifestyle was\N{\rChinese}狩猎采集的生活方式是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.48,0:50:14.64,English,,0,0,0,,so much more attractive to people, so much easier\N{\rChinese}如此更吸引人，且更容易
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.64,0:50:16.78,English,,0,0,0,,and attractive to people than the farming lifestyle.\N{\rChinese}比农耕生活更吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.34,0:50:21.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But the benefit of the farming lifestyle is that you had a religion.\N{\rChinese}好的？但农耕生活的好处在于它让你拥有宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.36,0:50:24.60,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why people chose ultimately to farm.\N{\rChinese}这就是人们最终选择农耕的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.32,0:50:27.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So that's it.\N{\rChinese}好了，就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.11,0:50:32.54,English,,0,0,0,,And next class, we'll continue this discussion about early religion.\N{\rChinese}接下来一节课，我们继续讨论早期宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.42,0:50:35.60,English,,0,0,0,,And how people developed these religious visions.\N{\rChinese}以及人们如何形成这些宗教观念。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.86,0:50:39.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So next class, we'll look at ice cave paintings\N{\rChinese}好了，下一节课我们来看看冰洞壁画。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.30,0:50:41.54,English,,0,0,0,,that goes back 40,000 years.\N{\rChinese}回溯四万年前。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.12,0:50:48.06,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that they practiced this sort of religion or something like this religion 40 to 50,000 years ago.\N{\rChinese}也就是说他们在四万五千年前有类似这种宗教的实践。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.20,0:50:50.24,English,,0,0,0,,And we know through ice cave paintings.\N{\rChinese}我们通过冰洞壁画知道这一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.24,0:50:53.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So\N{\rChinese}好的。那就
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.88,0:50:56.22,English,,0,0,0,,questions before we finish class.\N{\rChinese}在结束课堂之前还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.92,0:50:59.70,English,,0,0,0,,Is this clear to you guys?\N{\rChinese}这对你们来说清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.30,0:51:03.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Anything you're confused about?\N{\rChinese}好的？你有什么不懂的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.10,0:51:05.84,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions before we conclude?\N{\rChinese}在结束之前还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.72,0:51:19.12,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Do you see it more clearly?\N{\rChinese}好的。你看得更清楚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.58,0:51:25.86,English,,0,0,0,,And again, this is all on the internet, by the way.\N{\rChinese}再说一次，这些都在网上，顺便说一句。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.92,0:51:30.32,English,,0,0,0,,So if you're interested, you can go online and just read up more on Catahoyac.\N{\rChinese}如果你感兴趣，可以上网再多读点关于Catahoyac的资料。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.46,0:51:32.22,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? These places are very famous.\N{\rChinese}好的？这些地方非常有名气。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.36,0:51:34.32,English,,0,0,0,,We'll be discussing these places throughout the semester.\N{\rChinese}我们将在整个学期讨论这些地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.54,0:51:39.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Cabo Batepe, Jericho, and Catahoyac.\N{\rChinese}好吧？Cabo Batepe、Jericho 和 Catahoyac。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.22,0:51:47.08,English,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?.\N{\rChinese}请问一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.66,0:51:50.06,English,,0,0,0,,. We discussed all three.\N{\rChinese}我们已经讨论过这三处。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.24,0:51:52.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But I'm introducing you to these three places.\N{\rChinese}好的？但我先把这三处介绍给你们。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.68,0:51:55.52,English,,0,0,0,,In future classes, we'll go more in depth into these places.\N{\rChinese}在后续课程里，我们会更深入地探讨这些地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.60,0:51:59.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because Cabo Batepe is a very interesting place.\N{\rChinese}好的？因为Cabo Batepe是一个非常有趣的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.62,0:52:03.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And\N{\rChinese}好的？而且
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.34,0:52:07.56,English,,0,0,0,,we're only slowly discovering all that's there.\N{\rChinese}我们只是在慢慢发现那里的全部内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.90,0:52:10.54,English,,0,0,0,,Basically, we basically uncovered about 5% of Cabo Batepe.\N{\rChinese}基本上，我们已经发掘了Cabo Batepe的约5%。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.74,0:52:13.62,English,,0,0,0,,So over the next few decades, we'll know more.\N{\rChinese}接下来几十年，我们会了解更多。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.20,0:52:18.42,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.46,0:52:24.56,English,,0,0,0,,Any more questions? Okay.\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.64,0:52:29.56,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So next class, we will do Ice Cave paintings. .\N{\rChinese}好的。下节课我们来做冰洞壁画。
